---
// v0.9.3 dashboard route — release v0.9.3 of chepherd.
//
// What's new vs /v0.9.2/:
//   - A2A v1.0 spec-compliant method names (#291 P0 / PR #293):
//     message/send, tasks/get, tasks/pushNotificationConfig/set,
//     agent/getAuthenticatedExtendedCard, ... (pre-#291 PascalCase
//     names broke real-world interop with Google's A2A SDK).
//   - Per-flavor auth env (#225 H1 / PR #289): qwen→DASHSCOPE,
//     aider→ANTHROPIC|OPENAI, gemini-cli→GOOGLE wired through the
//     vault provider.
//   - PTY-driven CompletionDetector (#225 H2 / PR #290): A2A Task
//     state transitions driven by exit code + idle-pulse, not by
//     agent self-report.
//   - Persistence.Artifact + ArtifactRepository (#225 H3 / PR #298):
//     A2A v1.0 artifacts persisted in a normalized table with FK
//     CASCADE on Task delete.
//   - ES256 + JWKS publication (#225 B2 / PR #284 + #296 SQLite-busy
//     fix / PR #299): A2A peers can verify chepherd's JWTs via
//     /.well-known/jwks.json without out-of-band key sharing.
//   - 4 spec-compliant TokenValidator implementations (#225 B3-B6 /
//     PR #285): TrustList + mTLS + OAuth2 + apiKey.
//   - Federation: hosted peer registry + cross-instance routing +
//     multi-host walk DoD (#225 C1-C3 / PRs #280-#282).
//   - SSE binding for SendStreamingMessage + ResubscribeTask (#225
//     A2 / PR #283).
//   - Shepherd → Scrum Master rename across operator-facing surfaces
//     (#225 F2-F5 / PR #287 + #292 + #295 + #300).
//
// URL versioning rule (operator 2026-05-28): each release ships its
// own /vMAJOR.MINOR.PATCH/ route. /v0.9.2/ gets a 301 redirect to
// /v0.9.3/ for one release window per #297.
//
// This route mounts the existing Workspace shell with version="v0.9.3"
// so the header brand badge displays the right release.
import AuthGate from '../components/v09/AuthGate.svelte';
import '../styles/global.css';
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>chepherd v0.9.3 — workspace</title>
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
    <style>
      html, body { margin: 0; padding: 0; height: 100vh; overflow: hidden; background: #0a0a0a; }
      body { font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif; color: #f5f5f5; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <AuthGate client:load version="v0.9.3" />
  </body>
</html>
